Dia. 01 White Dies
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White \cf1\b fails for Black's trap\cf0\b0  if he connects at 1.
\par
\par After Black connects with 2, White can't live anymore.
\par
\par White 1 was not the vital point.
\par
\par }
