Dia. 02 There is a Problem
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 looks good.
\par If Black plays at 2, White goes out with 3 and makes one eye on each side.
\par
\par White lives up to 5. However there is a \cf1\b problem\cf0\b0  in this variation.
\par It is about Black 2.
\par
\par
